---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import castle from '../assets/lanju-fotografie-cvS-IDyGKTE-unsplash.jpg'
import knightOnHorse from '../assets/matt-benson-aymIPosVUKk-unsplash.jpg'
import armoredKnight from '../assets/matt-benson-mOfrRxFqWWU-unsplash.jpg'
import wolfhound from '../assets/natalia-gusakova-oJNOEJe_Ytw-unsplash.jpg'

const stats = [
  { value: '80', label: 'Years on the Grounds' },
  { value: '50+', label: 'Festivals & Tourneys' },
]
---

<section id="story" class="py-20 bg-base-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Born of Craft and Tradition</h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Since time out of mind, the tavern hath been the heart of the castle. It is the place
          where good folk doth settle in after the day's spectacle, letting the clamour of the
          grounds fade into warmth and fellowship. We have kept it thus, and shall do so while
          these walls yet stand.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          From the first thundering pass of the lists to the last torchlight of the evening
          festival, we remain open through all of it. Come hither for the spectacle, and stay
          for the company. This hath always been that manner of place.
        </p>

        <div class="flex gap-8 mt-8">
          {
            stats.map(({ value, label }) => (
              <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-4">
                <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary">{value}</p>
                <p class="text-base-content/60 text-sm mt-1">{label}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-square">
            <Image src={armoredKnight} alt="Knight in full armor holding a sword" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-square">
            <Image src={wolfhound} alt="Irish Wolfhound portrait" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-8">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-square">
            <Image src={castle} alt="Castle" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-square">
            <Image src={knightOnHorse} alt="Knight in armor on horseback" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
